rComments: Absolutely amazing. Being in her class is a gift. She facilitates an unbelievably important, engaging, and life-changing class.

What an amazing class. Robyn is one of the best profs at U of T. The readings were relevant, the lectures fascinating, and class atmosphere was wonderful. The readings are very very intense emotionally, but necessary to the course.

WGS373 Gender & Violence: Hands down one of the best profs @ UofT. She is THE most effective prof I have ever had. Life changing course & experience. Assignments were unique & fascinating. Grading was fair, with helpful comments. Her teaching style is memorable, upfront and powerful. You need to hear what she has to teach you (at least I did).
